citations:
    citation-adwd-the-spurned-suitor:
        source: source-adwd
        properties:
            locator: "The Spurned Suitor"
            text_from_source: "I need you to help me steal a dragon. … What I want, said the Tattered Prince, is Pentos."
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Quentyn Martell POV. Gerris Drinkwater contacts the Windblown company. Quentyn meets the Tattered Prince secretly in the cellar of the Purple Lotus inn near the spice market. Pretty Meris, Caggo Corpsekiller, and Denzo D'han also present. Quentyn offers to double the Yunkish payment and mentions Dornish gold held in Volantis banks. He reveals his plan to steal a dragon. The Tattered Prince demands Pentos as his price. Cletus and Will (Dornishmen killed en route) named, as is Maester Kedry. Yezzan zo Qaggaz mentioned as having died of the pale mare."
